    <h3 itemprop="headline">Shark attack survivor wakes from 10-day coma and shares first words with family at her hospital bedside</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Leah Stewart awoke from an induced coma after a shark attack at Coogee Beach in Sydney, sharing her first words &apos;I love you&apos; with her family.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/06/25/shark-attack-survivor-wakes-10-day-coma-shares-first-words-family-hospital-bedside/"  >(Fox News)</a>
