    <h3 itemprop="headline">Agentic AI security steals the spotlight at Confidential Computing Summit</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      For a decade, confidential computing has been chipping away at one of security’s hardest problems: data is well encrypted in transit and at rest, but when a processor works on it, that data sits in memory in the clear, exposed to anyone with privileged host access.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/06/25/agentic-ai-security-steals-the-spotlight-at-confidential-computing-summit/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
