        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Microsoft is turning Windows 11 into an AI operating system</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      For years, Microsoft has hyped Windows 11 cas an OS with AI, and the company is finally putting the building blocks in place for that transformation.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/06/26/microsoft-is-turning-windows-11-into-an-ai-operating-system/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
