    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Viktor Hovland wins Travelers in Monday playoff when Scheffler misses short birdie putt</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Viktor Hovland needed only one hole to beat Scottie Scheffler in a playoff at the Travelers Championship.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/06/29/viktor-hovland-wins-travelers-in-monday-playoff-when-scheffler-misses-short-birdie-putt/"  >(Doug Ferguson, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
