      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/06/29/americans-pride-in-us-history-and-democracy-drops-in-new-poll.webp" alt="Americans' pride in U.S. history and democracy drops, and fewer are proud to be American, polls find" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Americans' pride in U.S. history and democracy drops, and fewer are proud to be American, polls find</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A new AP-NORC poll finds that Americans have grown less proud of the country’s history or the way its democracy works over the past several years. That includes Americans' pride in the nation’s military and its political influence around the globe.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/29/americans-pride-in-us-history-and-democracy-drops-in-new-poll/"  >(The Associated Press, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 29 Jun 2026 13:43:34 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 29 Jun 2026 13:43:34 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Lindsay Whitehurst, Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/06/29/supreme-court-will-weigh-trump-backed-republican-push-to-enforce-arizona-voting-laws.webp" alt="Supreme Court will weigh Trump-backed Republican appeal to enforce Arizona voting laws" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Supreme Court will weigh Trump-backed Republican appeal to enforce Arizona voting laws</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Supreme Court says it will consider Arizona voting laws passed in the wake of the 2020 election that impose proof-of-citizenship requirements for voter registration and regular purging of state voter rolls.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/29/supreme-court-will-weigh-trump-backed-republican-push-to-enforce-arizona-voting-laws/"  >(Lindsay Whitehurst, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 29 Jun 2026 14:24:26 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 29 Jun 2026 14:24:26 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Mark Sherman, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/06/29/supreme-court-says-feds-cook-can-keep-her-job-for-now-but-it-upholds-other-trump-firings.webp" alt="Supreme Court says Fed&#8217;s Cook can keep her job for now, but it upholds other Trump firings" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Supreme Court says Fed&#8217;s Cook can keep her job for now, but it upholds other Trump firings</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Supreme Court says Federal Reserve governor Lisa Cook can remain in her job for now, a rebuke to President Donald Trump’s bid to wrest control of the nation’s central bank.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/29/supreme-court-says-feds-cook-can-keep-her-job-for-now-but-it-upholds-other-trump-firings/"  >(Mark Sherman, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
